<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Order_of_the_Bath&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="History">History</span></h2>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Order_of_the_Bath&action=edit&section=2.php.html" title="Edit section: Knights of the Bath">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Knights_of_the_Bath">Knights of the Bath</span></h3>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Edmund_blair_leighton_accolade.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Edmund_blair_leighton_accolade.jpg/220px-Edmund_blair_leighton_accolade.jpg" width="220" height="314" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Edmund_blair_leighton_accolade.jpg/330px-Edmund_blair_leighton_accolade.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Edmund_blair_leighton_accolade.jpg/440px-Edmund_blair_leighton_accolade.jpg 2x" /></a>
