<li id="cite_note-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchUK/Honours/OrderofStPatrick.aspx">"Order of St Patrick"</a>. Official website of the British monarchy<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchUK/Honours/OrderofStPatrick.aspx">http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchUK/Honours/OrderofStPatrick.aspx</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 6 December 2011</span>.</span></span></li>
