<li id="cite_note-Gazette58010-87"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Gazette58010_87-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Gazette58010_87-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><i><a href="The_London_Gazette" title="The London Gazette">The London Gazette</a></i>: <span class="PDFlink"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.london-gazette.co.uk/issues/58010/pages/8073">no. 58010. p. 8073</a></span>. 13 June 2006. Retrieved 2008-10-14.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-88"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-88">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Risk, p93</span></li>
